Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:23.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:44.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何處尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前這冷酷無情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理無從尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僅有骯髒的搶與奪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一場派對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命運縱橫交錯的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向著終點一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無論勝者或敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或許某物已然瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑問為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:23.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切盡皆消失在這片虛無之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}現在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高舉這份決心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}來吧  繼續BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:44.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束縛  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們只需變得瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需變得瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢或地獄  GO CRY GO
